            </div>
            <div class="tile is-child notification is-light box">
              <h1 class="title">Cloud Architecture</h1>
              <h2 class="subtitle">Cloud application design, management and <a href="#monitoring">monitoring</a> of a number of customer-facing services.</h2>
              <a href="#approov"><span class="tag is-dark is-rounded">Approov</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Operations -->
          <div class="tile is-parent is-4 is-vertical">
            <div class="tile is-child notification is-dark">
              <h1 class="title">Operations</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="tile is-child notification is-light box">
              <h1 class="title">Deployment</h1>
              <h2 class="subtitle">Well versed in deploying complex systems to AWS (CloudFormation, Terraform) and GCP (Kubernetes).</h2>
              <a href="#approov"><span class="tag is-dark is-rounded">Approov</span></a>
              <a href="#reverie"><span class="tag is-dark is-rounded">Reverie</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="tile is-child notification is-light box">
              <h1 class="title">Integration</h1>
              <h2 class="subtitle">Jenkins and Travis are my stomping grounds. Check out the <a href="#reverie">Reverie</a> PRs for a sneak peek of the standards I set myself.</h2>
