                    <span class="icon"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></span></a>&nbsp
                <span>
              </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="tile is-child notification is-light box">
              <h2 class="subtitle">A campaign tracker for tabletop RPGs.  Written in Django with &hearts;. Hit the GitHub icon to check out the source.</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
